about.description: A Python wrapper for the Pollster API
about.summary: A Python wrapper for the Pollster API

name: pollster
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pollster" %}
{% set version = "2.0.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: be83cceb4d6d9c8d9c2e31f21ddb360e29b6dfeff1948cba6f0ec0a3a2d7bfb4 

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - certifi>=14.05.14
    - six>=1.8.0
    - python-dateutil>=2.5.3
    - urllib3>=1.15.1
    - pandas>=0.19.1

test:
  imports:
    - pollster

about:
  home: https://elections.huffingtonpost.com/pollster
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A Python wrapper for the Pollster API'
  description: 'A Python wrapper for the Pollster API'
  doc_url: https://elections.huffingtonpost.com/pollster/api/v2
  dev_url: https://github.com/huffpostdata/python-pollster

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - SylvainCorlay
